{"type":null,"faqId":49867,"title":"华为智能手表_手表耐刮伤吗？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body17004965\"><ul id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329062__ul45314905\"><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329062__li18826965\">华为智能手表采用316L冷锻不锈钢工艺，比非冷锻普通材质坚硬40%，非常坚固，请放心使用。</li><li id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329062__li35224963\">手表的屏幕是蓝宝石材质，该材质硬度较高，是不易磨损的材料，正常的使用不会被划伤，但是仍然要避免受到严重撞击或者掉落地面，避免尖锐器物划刻磕碰等。如小刀划、刻、石头磕、碰等。</li></ul></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":494,"faqType":"维护与保养","useful":4,"unUseful":4,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329062","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Product-Maintenance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448615861000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":110,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"防护，刮伤，防刮","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}